<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[420, 157, 532, 173]]<|/det|>
## 1. ALGEBRA  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[74, 186, 222, 203]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[111, 215, 354, 232]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\),  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[395, 233, 556, 266]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}.\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[74, 286, 210, 303]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[240, 305, 710, 344]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1} b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2} b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r} b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n},\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[111, 351, 467, 388]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\) .  

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[384, 447, 562, 465]]<|/det|>
## 2. TRIGONOMETRY

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[401, 505, 546, 572]]<|/det|>
\[\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1\] \[\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\] \[\csc^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[74, 599, 223, 616]]<|/det|>
Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[386, 621, 561, 650]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C}\]  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[386, 670, 561, 688]]<|/det|>
\[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc\cos A\]  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[420, 696, 530, 724]]<|/det|>
\[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc\sin A\]
